investments of Pounds 517,000 (Pounds 2.11m).
Earnings per share emerged at 6.3p (8.2p). No final dividend is proposed
making 1p (4.5p); however, a special interim distribution of 5p is payable
under the proposed buy-out from Idwal Williams.
